/-Installation Instructions-\

Merge the included cstrike folder with your own (namely: C:\Program Files (x86)\Steam\steamapps\USERNAME\counter-strike source\cstrike,
replace USERNAME with your steam username used to sign in) and you're done. Nothing else NEEDS to be done.
==============================

spent several hours of my time trying to do hard work with this map, perfect it. If you don't like it, sorry to
dissapoint you. If you DO like it, please feel free to suggest it to other Texture City servers.
